{"tid":1673204,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"比埋memo紙你既cafe，請大家幫手懲罰一下佢","createTime":"2019-10-24T13:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T15:23:48.000Z","uid":158984,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff4c27a621e264f1bb7f41ddfc1a82cc262d267","tid":1673204,"uid":158984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"呢間鋪頭上左黃店list，但今日同朋友上去食，計埋我地得2枱客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我嗌左個韓式卡邦尼意粉但我唔記得影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辣辣地幾特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友嗌左個忌廉三文魚意粉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DmZXjcK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDmZXjcK.jpg&h=87990f7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清清地幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />包左杯野飲138<br />\n我地嗌左杯蜂蜜蘋果茶，飲到底竟然有蘋果粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都幾驚喜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDy5s8T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDy5s8T.png&h=cb397130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地有board game可以比你地上去玩，除左比較普遍既遊戲，亦都有啲比較偏門既boardgame，員工會好親切咁教你地玩，亦會介紹啲遊戲比你地玩<br />\n鋪頭窗口有連儂牆比大家貼文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vHLWzN4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvHLWzN4.png&h=4f50a466&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eDT9amw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeDT9amw.png&h=04af2361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完飯佢地仲會比memo紙你去痴連儂牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DAeHvnT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDAeHvnT.png&h=72cd3d65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0XQfQnY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0XQfQnY.png&h=47dd09db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我就畫左隻好醜既腦魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJu4JJC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJu4JJC.png&h=7d1373a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原諒我啲字好醜同埋我既小學生畫功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間餐廳位於旺角一條巷仔既大廈入面都幾難搵，不過打比佢地問路佢地會教你點行過去<br />\n<br />\n餐廳名：棋吧<br />\r地址： <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0nfm600~uHsTbAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0nfm600~uHsTbAw&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNnKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=4233867e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0nfm600~uHsTbAw</a><br />\n<br />\n大家朋友聚會傾計不妨考慮懲罰一下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b2db5f8a3cd6477c3a2c278dc587e48bd014cf","tid":1673204,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/guewjRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FguewjRY.jpg&h=ac95176a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a7e80ede2cb348725db7ec6172620602d6a8b208","tid":1673204,"uid":330274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"下星期去食先"},{"pid":"f23260985dc1d96004ed6bb561b52633915b2d8b","tid":1673204,"uid":158984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:08:22.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8a59bcda5f9a7cfd76777e84fdd48e4b0921fd","tid":1673204,"uid":158984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:08:36.000Z","msg":"先推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756e8379ed90e8641600fbf6f4ce94d8aa0ae8