Z","msg":"真黃店318都照比啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e049b4e5e97f0e60de0363f52e4289b859e7d93c","tid":1673204,"uid":158984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2ba823fe7f99a235750d895d2df49c35aa926be","tid":1673204,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:57:02.000Z","msg":"真黃店318都照比啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:23:48.000Z","msg":"True<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得大家做到幾多咪做，黃店就係需要懲罰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c13X4gz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc13X4gz.png&h=c730b97c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢上左黃色小店ig list<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6HdQEQm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6HdQEQm.png&h=5889882a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sAfWAo0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsAfWAo0.png&h=3fb312af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢個ig page都好多文宣架<br />\n<br />\n都係個句，我係老細想借啲意宣傳既話出出下街比狗拉"}]}